<div class="flex-container solve">
  <div class="flex-header">
    <h1 class="headline-text">Solve The Mystery</h1>
    <h1 class="subhead-text">(of how Ted is in office)</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-body">
    <div class="solve-the-mystery">
      <div class="solve-the-mystery-steps">
        <h3 class="solve-the-mystery-steps-header">If You Live in Texas:</h3>
        <ol class="solve-the-mystery-steps-list">
          <li>
            <a href="http://www.votetexas.gov/register-to-vote/" {{action 'trackRegisterClick' preventDefault=false}}>Register To Vote</a> or make sure you are registered!
          </li>
          <li>
            Show up and vote for people who aren't Ted Cruz! It's easy, and there's a voting location close to where you live.
          </li>
          <li>
            Find a friend who thinks voting is dumb and drag them along to vote (and register) with you.
          </li>
        </ol>

        <h3 class="solve-the-mystery-steps-header">If You Are A Human Living On This Planet:</h3>
        <ol class="solve-the-mystery-steps-list">
          <li>
            Vote for people who aren't like Ted Cruz!
          </li>
          <li>
            Encourage and nag your Texas friends to show up and vote.
          </li>
          <li>
            Spread the word about Cruz Clues!

            <div class="sharing-buttons">
              {{#fb-share-button url="https://cruzclues.com" quote="The evidence is all here."}}Share{{/fb-share-button}}
              {{#twitter-share-button title="The evidence is all here." url="https://cruzclues.com" hashtags="cruzclues"}}Tweet{{/twitter-share-button}}
              {{#gplus-share-button url="http://cruzclues.com"}}Share{{/gplus-share-button}}
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-action">
    {{#link-to 'random'}}Research The Clues Again{{/link-to}}
  </div>

  {{site-footer class="flex-footer"}}
</div>
